          "content": "\n                    <div class=\"mb-6\">\n                        <h3 class=\"text-lg font-semibold mb-4\">GDPR Fundamentals for AI Systems</h3>\n                        <p class=\"mb-4\">As your legal compliance instructor with 10 years of experience in data protection law, I'll guide you through the complex intersection of GDPR and AI systems.</p>\n                        \n                        <div class=\"bg-blue-50 p-4 rounded-lg mb-6\">\n                            <h4 class=\"font-semibold text-blue-900 mb-2\">üéØ Learning Objectives</h4>\n                            <ul class=\"text-blue-800 space-y-1\">\n                                <li>‚Ä¢ Master GDPR principles as they apply to AI systems</li>\n                                <li>‚Ä¢ Understand legal bases for AI data processing</li>\n                                <li>‚Ä¢ Learn to conduct privacy impact assessments</li>\n                                <li>‚Ä¢ Implement privacy by design principles</li>\n                            </ul>\n                        </div>\n                        \n                        <img src=\"/gdpr-rights-infographic.png\" alt=\"GDPR Individual Rights\" class=\"w-full max-h-96 object-contain mx-auto mb-6 rounded-lg shadow-md\" />\n                        \n                        <h4 class=\"font-semibold mb-3\">Core GDPR Principles for AI</h4>\n                        <div class=\"overflow-x-auto mb-6\">\n                            <table class=\"min-w-full bg-white border border-gray-200\">\n                                <thead class=\"bg-orange-500 text-white\">\n                                    <tr>\n                                        <th class=\"px-4 py-3 text-left\">GDPR Principle</th>\n                                        <th class=\"px-4 py-3 text-left\">AI Application</th>\n                                        <th class=\"px-4 py-3 text-left\">Compliance Challenge</th>\n                                        <th class=\"px-4 py-3 text-left\">Solution Approach</th>\n                                    </tr>\n                                </thead>\n                                <tbody class=\"divide-y divide-gray-200\">\n                                    <tr class=\"hover:bg-gray-50\">\n                                        <td class=\"px-4 py-3 font-medium\">Lawfulness</td>\n                                        <td class=\"px-4 py-3\">Legal basis for AI processing</td>\n                                        <td class=\"px-4 py-3\">Evolving AI purposes</td>\n                                        <td class=\"px-4 py-3\">Legitimate interests assessment</td>\n                                    </tr>\n                                    <tr class=\"hover:bg-gray-50\">\n                                        <td class=\"px-4 py-3 font-medium\">Transparency</td>\n                                        <td class=\"px-4 py-3\">Explainable AI decisions</td>\n                                        <td class=\"px-4 py-3\">Black box algorithms</td>\n                                        <td class=\"px-4 py-3\">Meaningful information provision</td>\n                                    </tr>\n                                    <tr class=\"hover:bg-gray-50\">\n                                        <td class=\"px-4 py-3 font-medium\">Data Minimization</td>\n                                        <td class=\"px-4 py-3\">Minimal data for AI training</td>\n                                        <td class=\"px-4 py-3\">Big data requirements</td>\n                                        <td class=\"px-4 py-3\">Privacy-preserving techniques</td>\n                                    </tr>\n                                    <tr class=\"hover:bg-gray-50\">\n                                        <td class=\"px-4 py-3 font-medium\">Purpose Limitation</td>\n                                        <td class=\"px-4 py-3\">Specific AI use cases</td>\n                                        <td class=\"px-4 py-3\">Feature discovery</td>\n                                        <td class=\"px-4 py-3\">Compatible use assessment</td>\n                                    </tr>\n                                </tbody>\n                            </table>\n                        </div>\n                        \n                        <div class=\"bg-red-50 p-4 rounded-lg mb-4\">\n                            <h4 class=\"font-semibold text-red-900 mb-2\">‚ö†Ô∏è Critical Compliance Point</h4>\n                            <p class=\"text-red-800\">Article 22 prohibits solely automated decision-making with legal or significant effects. This directly impacts AI systems used for hiring, lending, or other consequential decisions.</p>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                    "
